title: [Whistler's Pass, Grassy Field]
description: A small tree lies where it fell across the trail, its foliage still a dark green in the darkness, fighting decay.  A brown vine snakes its way around the tree trunk like a snake crushing its prey.  The chill of the higher regions fades as the field descends to the north.
